	  -- OUR SCOPE IS LIMITED TO PYTHON SCRIPTING FOR DEVOPS ACTIVITIES 
	  -- OOP focuses on the concepts of classes, objects, inheritance, encapsulation, polymorphism, and abstraction.
	  
	 

